    "long_instructions": "Create a song using the provided prechorus and chorus tracks from Katy Perry's Fireworks. You will need to add appropriate bass and lead tracks to the chorus - you can decide what to add! Choose whatever you think makes the song sound great!\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary>Validation Details</summary>\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Condition</td>\r\n\t  <td>S/F?</td>\r\n\t  <td>Message</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>3 Play Together Blocks with bass and lead in each</td>\r\n\t  <td>S</td>\r\n\t  <td>Nice job adding bass and lead to your song!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Less than 3 play together</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td>Make sure you have 3 play together blocks!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>At least one play together is missing bass or lead</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td>Make sure all your play together blocks have both bass and lead!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n</details>\r\n",
